      • isInitialized

        io.reactivex.Single<java.lang.Boolean> isInitialized()

        Method returns boolean state, if terminal manager is initialized. Basically it means, that TerminalManager.getSelectedExtension and TerminalManager.getSelectedDevice return some value and TerminalManager.discoverDevices was properly called.

        See Also:
        TerminalManager.getSelectedExtension, TerminalManager.getSelectedDevice, TerminalManager.discoverDevices
